title: Schools out for Biden
description: Fellas joke about Biden's COVID mismanagement and a seven foot tall man before playing a fresh game of King of the Hill. Dr. Mehmet Oz joins the progrum for an interview about his campaign for U.S. Senate from Pennsylvania.
